text: Fulton is a census-designated place (CDP) in Sonoma County, California, United States. Fulton is just to the north of the city limits of Santa Rosa, and north-northeast of Sebastopol. The population as of the 2020 U.S. Census was 551. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in Sonoma County, California
title: Fulton, California
